making a mess of the document.

555
00:44:55,440 --> 00:44:56,560
I'm sorry.

556
00:44:59,240 --> 00:45:00,200
Yai!

557
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:04,000
Lek!

558
00:45:04,120 --> 00:45:06,400
Eh? Are you here as well, Jom?

559
00:45:08,520 --> 00:45:09,360
Yes, sir.

560
00:45:10,440 --> 00:45:12,120
Are you helping Yai with his work?

561
00:45:14,120 --> 00:45:17,520
Oh! Didn't I tell you, Khun Lek,

562
00:45:17,520 --> 00:45:20,040
not to get into this house
when your brother is working?

563
00:45:20,440 --> 00:45:22,760
I just wanted him to draw me a picture.

564
00:45:23,680 --> 00:45:26,040
I don't know why you're getting in my way.

565
00:45:28,240 --> 00:45:29,600
That's fine, Prik.

566
00:45:30,440 --> 00:45:34,320
So, please draw me a picture.

567
00:45:34,600 --> 00:45:38,720
Please, Yai.

568
00:46:04,720 --> 00:46:05,320
I'm done.

569
00:46:08,520 --> 00:46:09,880
How is it, Lek?

570
00:46:10,400 --> 00:46:13,320
