571
00:46:14,880 --> 00:46:16,240
Not pretty at all.

572
00:46:22,520 --> 00:46:25,280
Well... Khun Yai,

573
00:46:26,480 --> 00:46:29,000
can I see it?

574
00:46:29,880 --> 00:46:33,720
Well...

575
00:46:34,920 --> 00:46:36,000
I don't think you should see it.

576
00:46:37,000 --> 00:46:40,360
Please. Just for a moment.

577
00:46:43,320 --> 00:46:45,000
Don't be shy.

578
00:46:46,080 --> 00:46:46,760
Please.

579
00:46:59,400 --> 00:47:02,000
Look! I knew it!

580
00:47:02,440 --> 00:47:05,600
I didn't say anything, did I?

581
00:47:05,600 --> 00:47:08,200
It's cute.

582
00:47:11,120 --> 00:47:12,120
Khun Lek,

583
00:47:13,080 --> 00:47:15,120
if you don't like it,

584
00:47:15,520 --> 00:47:16,920
can I draw you a new one?

585
00:47:17,000 --> 00:47:18,160
Can you draw?

586
00:47:18,440 --> 00:47:19,080
Yes, I can.

587
00:47:19,800 --> 00:47:21,280
What kind of airplane do you want?

588
00:47:21,520 --> 00:47:23,520
You can tell me, so I can draw you one.

589
00:47:24,240 --> 00:47:26,000
I don't want an airplane any longer.

590
00:47:27,600 --> 00:47:30,240
Ah! You're looking after my piglet.

591
00:47:31,120 --> 00:47:34,480
So can you draw me the piglet

592
00:47:34,480 --> 00:47:36,360
that you're looking after for me?

593
00:47:36,800 --> 00:47:38,360
I will show it to Father.

594
00:47:39,400 --> 00:47:40,240
Of course.

595
00:48:22,920 --> 00:48:24,200
Do you like this, Khun Lek?

596
00:48:28,920 --> 00:48:29,720
Khun Lek!

597
00:48:36,120 --> 00:48:37,240
Mr. Jom!

598
00:48:39,680 --> 00:48:40,480
Uncle Tan!

599
00:48:44,400 --> 00:48:45,200
Uncle Tan!

600
00:48:47,280 --> 00:48:48,040
Uncle Tan!

601
00:48:51,080 --> 00:48:51,840
Uncle Tan!

602
00:48:53,240 --> 00:48:54,160
Uncle Tan!

603
00:48:59,640 --> 00:49:00,720
Jom!

604
00:49:06,200 --> 00:49:07,480
Jom!

605
00:49:09,240 --> 00:49:10,080
Jom!

606
00:49:12,400 --> 00:49:13,120
Jom!

607
00:49:15,000 --> 00:49:15,920
Jom!

608
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:21,500
Jom!

609
00:49:25,920 --> 00:49:28,080
Oh! Khun Lek!

610
00:49:29,120 --> 00:49:30,080
I'm sorry.

611
00:49:31,120 --> 00:49:32,120
What's going on?

612
00:49:38,000 --> 00:49:38,920
What are you guys doing?

613
00:49:43,920 --> 00:49:44,720
Nothing.

614
00:49:45,200 --> 00:49:47,680
Lek has just got Jom
to draw him the piglet.

615
00:49:50,400 --> 00:49:51,800
So what brings you here?

616
00:49:51,800 --> 00:49:55,240
You rarely visit this place.

617
00:49:55,520 --> 00:49:58,840
James told me that you could train a pig.

618
00:49:59,720 --> 00:50:01,760
So I want to see it with my own two eyes.

619
00:50:02,080 --> 00:50:04,480
Right. He's very good at it.

620
00:50:04,726 --> 00:50:06,126
He's training my piglet.

621
00:50:07,120 --> 00:50:10,040
Why do you want to train your pig?

622
00:50:11,920 --> 00:50:12,960
Or...

623
00:50:13,080 --> 00:50:16,120
Yes. I want Jom to train my pig

624
00:50:16,145 --> 00:50:17,825
for the race on Christmas Day.

625
00:50:17,920 --> 00:50:20,320
If I win,

626
00:50:20,840 --> 00:50:23,320
I will give him a huge prize, I think.

627
00:50:25,720 --> 00:50:27,120
I'm afraid that is
not going to happen.

628
00:50:28,720 --> 00:50:32,920
Now he is my majordomo.

629
00:50:36,720 --> 00:50:38,120
Why did you choose him?!

630
00:50:38,520 --> 00:50:42,120
I thought that this job suited him.

631
00:50:42,520 --> 00:50:46,800
So can I get him to train
my pig for the race, Yai?

632
00:50:47,120 --> 00:50:50,320
I can give him a special wage.

633
00:50:51,120 --> 00:50:52,080
I'm afraid not.

634
00:50:52,920 --> 00:50:55,720
Now he's got so much work to do.

635
00:50:55,920 --> 00:50:59,520
I think you'd better find someone else.

636
00:51:02,520 --> 00:51:03,600
Fine, Yai.

637
00:51:06,560 --> 00:51:08,360
I will never mess with your person.

638
00:51:08,840 --> 00:51:10,120
But keep it mind,

639
00:51:10,520 --> 00:51:13,800
what I'm doing will
bring fame to our house.

640
00:51:13,920 --> 00:51:16,920
If you don't support me, that's fine.

641
00:51:31,520 --> 00:51:33,640
Where are you taking me, Prik?

642
00:51:34,320 --> 00:51:35,400
Please let me go.

643
00:51:39,600 --> 00:51:40,480
Khun Yai.

644
00:51:40,880 --> 00:51:41,920
I have told you, Khun Yai,

645
00:51:41,920 --> 00:51:44,720
that Jom will bring trouble to you someday.

646
00:51:46,320 --> 00:51:48,000
But nothing has yet happened, right?

647
00:51:48,320 --> 00:51:49,520
I can manage it.

648
00:51:49,720 --> 00:51:51,120
Not now.

649
00:51:51,320 --> 00:51:53,760
But please think about it.

650
00:51:53,760 --> 00:51:55,280
Mr. Robert is Khun Luang's favorite.

651
00:51:55,920 --> 00:51:57,800
If he can convince him,

652
00:51:57,920 --> 00:51:59,520
what will do you then?

653
00:52:01,400 --> 00:52:06,360
Prik, I understand that you worry about me,

654
00:52:07,120 --> 00:52:10,720
but can you also trust me

655
00:52:10,720 --> 00:52:12,240
to make my own decisions?

656
00:52:14,120 --> 00:52:15,880
I'm not a kid any more.

657
00:52:19,520 --> 00:52:23,480
And you know that, up to this time,

658
00:52:27,120 --> 00:52:28,200
I...

659
00:52:32,120 --> 00:52:36,400
I haven't had many chances
to choose things for myself.

660
00:52:45,120 --> 00:52:46,960
If you mention this point,

661
00:52:50,120 --> 00:52:52,120
how can I resist you?

662
00:52:58,120 --> 00:52:59,640
Thank you so much, Prik.

663
00:53:19,400 --> 00:53:20,200
The liquor is gone!

664
00:53:41,120 --> 00:53:42,120
What is wrong with him?

665
00:53:42,520 --> 00:53:44,800
Drinking all the liquor
and disturbing others.

666
00:53:45,640 --> 00:53:48,360
Leave him like that. He
looks insane, actually.

667
00:53:50,200 --> 00:53:52,920
By the way, how come you're this rich?!

668
00:53:53,480 --> 00:53:54,520
You're treating us to
liquor every single day.

669
00:53:54,520 --> 00:53:57,920
I was about to ask you, too.

670
00:53:58,640 --> 00:54:01,680
I'm just... working for a foreign master.

671
00:54:02,824 --> 00:54:05,560
What kind of work? Can we do it, too?

672
00:54:05,680 --> 00:54:08,000
Just the work to kick out his
tenants who can't pay the rental.

673
00:54:08,920 --> 00:54:11,720
I did something at a woman's
house until she couldn't stand it

674
00:54:11,720 --> 00:54:14,600
and finally left. Nothing much...

675
00:54:14,840 --> 00:54:16,520
You bastard!

676
00:54:16,880 --> 00:54:19,520
You don't even share
your job with friends like us!

677
00:54:20,080 --> 00:54:22,080
Come on! It's dangerous!

678
00:54:22,200 --> 00:54:23,640
You don't need to know that.

679
00:54:24,520 --> 00:54:27,640
What a shame! The daughter of that house

680
00:54:28,373 --> 00:54:31,893
was bloody pretty! Now she
must've already gotten married, I think.

681
00:54:35,120 --> 00:54:37,400
What the hell is wrong
with you from the start?

682
00:54:37,480 --> 00:54:38,920
Then what the hell is
wrong with you bastards?

683
00:54:40,200 --> 00:54:42,920
We're just talking. Not
even your bloody business.

684
00:54:43,800 --> 00:54:45,360
So what were you bloody talking about?

685
00:54:45,600 --> 00:54:48,600
Who were you talking about?!

686
00:54:49,920 --> 00:54:51,120
This bastard!

687
00:55:00,520 --> 00:55:01,160
Let go of me!

688
00:55:12,160 --> 00:55:13,200
Khun Lek.

689
00:55:13,800 --> 00:55:17,120
I'm not playing anymore,
please stop running.

690
00:55:17,720 --> 00:55:19,520
Oh, be careful!

691
00:55:20,800 --> 00:55:22,200
Khun Lek.

692
00:55:23,000 --> 00:55:24,800
Oh my, Khun Lek.

693
00:55:26,716 --> 00:55:29,866
No more running, you'll slip and fall.

694
00:55:30,080 --> 00:55:30,920
Khun Lek.

695
00:55:31,320 --> 00:55:34,400
I'm not playing anymore.

696
00:55:38,520 --> 00:55:39,720
Oh?

697
00:55:39,920 --> 00:55:40,720
Dad.

698
00:55:42,200 --> 00:55:43,520
Hey, has school closed yet?

699
00:55:43,800 --> 00:55:45,800
Yes, I've been home for a while.

700
00:55:47,320 --> 00:55:48,320
Come here. Come here.

701
00:55:48,840 --> 00:55:50,000
I missed you so much.

702
00:55:50,720 --> 00:55:51,920
Sit, sit.

703
00:55:58,120 --> 00:56:00,360
Chan, put away my belongings.

704
00:56:00,560 --> 00:56:01,600
Yes, sir.

705
00:56:04,400 --> 00:56:05,920
Have you finished your work, sir?

706
00:56:07,600 --> 00:56:09,320
Everyone is perfect here, Kaekai?

707
00:56:09,440 --> 00:56:13,120
Yes, it is. There's nothing to worry about.

708
00:56:14,920 --> 00:56:17,120
It seems like I've got some good news

709
00:56:17,120 --> 00:56:18,640
to tell you, Kaekai.

710
00:56:22,080 --> 00:56:24,760
I'd better tell you all at
once when we're together.

711
00:56:26,120 --> 00:56:27,000
Father,

712
00:56:27,880 --> 00:56:29,760
I've got something to show you.

713
00:56:30,720 --> 00:56:31,800
What's that?

714
00:56:33,520 --> 00:56:36,320
Prik, get that drawing for me.

715
00:56:37,880 --> 00:56:38,640
Yes, sir.

716
00:56:43,410 --> 00:56:45,120
You weren't a stubborn boy, right?

717
00:56:51,400 --> 00:56:52,400
Here, Father.

718
00:56:56,840 --> 00:57:00,480
Did you do it yourself?!
Have you got such talent?!

719
00:57:01,240 --> 00:57:02,320
No, I didn't.

720
00:57:03,360 --> 00:57:05,240
It's Yai's new majordomo.

721
00:57:05,240 --> 00:57:06,400
He drew it for me.

722
00:57:08,320 --> 00:57:09,720
A new majordomo?

723
00:57:33,320 --> 00:57:36,440
Who is he?

724
00:57:36,600 --> 00:57:39,280
My name is Jom, sir.

725
00:57:39,760 --> 00:57:40,880
That's it?

726
00:57:41,520 --> 00:57:43,120
And where do you come from?

727
00:57:44,080 --> 00:57:46,400
Well, I...

728
00:57:48,120 --> 00:57:49,640
He can't remember, Father.

729
00:57:50,440 --> 00:57:51,520
He was lost.

730
00:57:51,920 --> 00:57:53,960
So that was how you just let him in?

731
00:57:55,000 --> 00:57:55,840
Yes, Father.

732
00:57:56,320 --> 00:57:57,720
But don't worry.

733
00:57:58,520 --> 00:58:02,640
Nothing bad has happened
yet since he lived here.

734
00:58:04,320 --> 00:58:07,640
What if he caused any trouble?

735
00:58:08,600 --> 00:58:09,760
I'd be responsible for it myself.

736
00:58:10,080 --> 00:58:13,040
Huh! You?

737
00:58:13,400 --> 00:58:14,040
Yes, Father.

738
00:58:15,440 --> 00:58:17,400
I'd be responsible for it myself.

739
00:58:17,920 --> 00:58:22,040
Finally, you've said this word
after leaving me waiting for so long.

740
00:58:28,040 --> 00:58:29,800
I've inspected the upper floor.

741
00:58:30,120 --> 00:58:31,800
Everything is good, sir.

742
00:58:32,120 --> 00:58:35,360
There are no weapons or
any deadly objects in his room.

743
00:58:36,080 --> 00:58:37,240
Do you see that, Father?

744
00:58:38,080 --> 00:58:39,240
He has done nothing wrong.

745
00:58:39,720 --> 00:58:41,120
If you think so,

746
00:58:42,520 --> 00:58:44,400
why don't you get him to
work a little bit to see if it works?

747
00:58:49,320 --> 00:58:50,320
Yes, I can.

748
00:59:13,520 --> 00:59:14,240
I'm finished, sir.

749
00:59:33,000 --> 00:59:34,280
Not too bad.

750
00:59:37,320 --> 00:59:40,000
But I still don't trust him that much.

751
00:59:41,520 --> 00:59:42,640
Why not, Father?

752
00:59:44,320 --> 00:59:46,200
Be it Thai or English documents,

753
00:59:46,640 --> 00:59:50,440
Jom can do them all.

754
00:59:51,320 --> 00:59:53,760
So doesn't it mean that he
can do everything like Chan?

755
00:59:54,112 --> 00:59:57,152
He can't even remember his own history,

756
00:59:58,513 --> 01:00:01,233
so how can you trust this kind of person?

757
01:00:02,120 --> 01:00:05,840
So I have to choose only
what you have chosen for me.

758
01:00:06,080 --> 01:00:07,080
Is that right, Father?

759
01:00:08,920 --> 01:00:11,440
When it comes to my own business,

760
01:00:13,120 --> 01:00:14,440
you seem to have some problems.

761
01:00:14,520 --> 01:00:15,520
You!

762
01:00:18,240 --> 01:00:20,760
Now I don't want to rebuke you too much,

763
01:00:21,840 --> 01:00:24,400
or I won't be in the mood
to tell you my good news.

764
01:00:25,080 --> 01:00:27,400
Uncle Dech will dine with us here tonight.

765
01:00:27,920 --> 01:00:29,240
Prepare yourself.

766
01:00:29,600 --> 01:00:32,320
Tell your majordomo
to prepare you an outfit.

767
01:00:36,600 --> 01:00:37,600
I'm leaving.

768
01:01:13,240 --> 01:01:16,440
Are you still upset, Jom?

769
01:01:17,720 --> 01:01:18,760
A bit, sir.

770
01:01:21,720 --> 01:01:26,000
I never though that Khun Luang...

771
01:01:26,000 --> 01:01:30,400
Well, your father. I never
thought he would be this strict.

772
01:01:34,520 --> 01:01:37,800
That's normal. You'll
get used to it after a while.

773
01:01:44,933 --> 01:01:49,413
So why did you have to help me that much?

774
01:01:52,120 --> 01:01:56,840
As I said earlier,

775
01:01:59,080 --> 01:02:00,680
I just want to choose what I want

776
01:02:04,080 --> 01:02:07,040
and go by my wish sometimes.

777
01:02:24,800 --> 01:02:26,000
The suit is better.

778
01:02:35,240 --> 01:02:39,880
You can go to bed before me tonight.

779
01:02:40,640 --> 01:02:42,000
I might come back late.

780
01:02:42,120 --> 01:02:43,200
You don't need to wait.

781
01:02:43,720 --> 01:02:44,720
Take a rest, then.

782
01:02:47,520 --> 01:02:48,120
Yes, sir.

783
01:02:50,120 --> 01:02:53,240
I'm going.

784
01:03:30,600 --> 01:03:31,440
Jom...

785
01:03:36,240 --> 01:03:37,400
Jom...

786
01:03:41,080 --> 01:03:41,720
Khun Yai!

787
01:03:41,720 --> 01:03:42,520
Khun Yai!

788
01:03:44,720 --> 01:03:45,840
Jom...

789
01:03:46,720 --> 01:03:47,720
Khun Yai

790
01:03:59,360 --> 01:04:00,520
Jom...

791
01:04:01,920 --> 01:04:02,640
Yes?

792
01:04:02,640 --> 01:04:06,680
I'm drunk, I suppose.

793
01:04:09,840 --> 01:04:12,640
Yes, you are. Very drunk, actually.

794
01:04:18,640 --> 01:04:21,480
So let me take you to your room.

795
01:04:21,480 --> 01:04:22,240
Slowly get up.

796
01:04:22,240 --> 01:04:23,960
Hold me tight.

797
01:04:26,960 --> 01:04:28,080
Ok

798
01:04:28,080 --> 01:04:29,120
Walk slowly.

799
01:04:42,760 --> 01:04:47,840
Khun Yai, wait a minute.

800
01:04:49,320 --> 01:04:50,320
I'm going to turn on the light.

801
01:04:59,840 --> 01:05:02,440
Khun Yai, please go up and lie on your bed!

802
01:05:10,080 --> 01:05:10,880
Khun Yai!

803
01:05:11,000 --> 01:05:11,680
Jom...

804
01:05:13,120 --> 01:05:13,680
Yes?

805
01:05:17,120 --> 01:05:18,920
Here is my Jom...

806
01:05:21,720 --> 01:05:26,640
I thought I was dreaming...

807
01:05:27,120 --> 01:05:28,320
Dreaming?

808
01:05:30,080 --> 01:05:32,920
I think I'd better bring a
wet cloth to clean your body.

809
01:05:38,320 --> 01:05:39,000
Yes?

810
01:05:40,520 --> 01:05:41,360
Jom...

811
01:05:48,800 --> 01:05:50,760
Be with me here...

812
01:05:51,807 --> 01:05:53,127
Don't go...

813
01:05:56,720 --> 01:06:02,360
You drink often, don't you?

814
01:06:07,720 --> 01:06:09,000
Not really...

815
01:06:11,920 --> 01:06:16,640
I drink at times...

816
01:06:18,320 --> 01:06:25,520
Did you have a fight with Khun Luang?

817
01:06:56,440 --> 01:06:57,400
Jom...

818
01:07:04,060 --> 01:07:05,780
Where is your mind wandering?

819
01:07:08,080 --> 01:07:09,120
No, it's not.

820
01:07:12,720 --> 01:07:18,480
Are you thinking of your departed lover?

821
01:07:23,440 --> 01:07:30,080
I... I don't have such a thing, sir.

822
01:07:32,120 --> 01:07:34,000
Not a single one?

823
01:07:41,000 --> 01:07:42,400
It was ended, actually.

824
01:07:48,000 --> 01:07:52,160
You're really drunk, aren't you?

825
01:07:58,640 --> 01:08:05,640
Not a drop of liquor to interfere,
drunk on love's celestial bliss

826
01:08:09,080 --> 01:08:14,240
I've tried to resist
this sweet intoxication

827
01:08:17,120 --> 01:08:23,440
no matter how drunk I am,
sobriety comes with the morning light

828
01:08:27,086 --> 01:08:33,006
Drunk on love, my
heart undone every night

829
01:08:42,520 --> 01:08:44,840
You seem to be following the steps
of the poet, Phraya Sisunthonwohan.

830
01:08:45,000 --> 01:08:47,720
Soon you'll have about
10 wives under your arm.

831
01:08:51,120 --> 01:08:52,320
Lovers?

832
01:08:54,800 --> 01:08:59,520
One is enough for me.

833
01:09:43,920 --> 01:09:45,000
Drawings?

834
01:09:45,120 --> 01:09:47,000
Just some drawings?

835
01:09:47,280 --> 01:09:49,480
I thought it would be something
more valuable than these.

836
01:10:27,480 --> 01:10:31,560
(Next Episode) Did I accidentally
do something to you last night?

837
01:10:32,040 --> 01:10:34,360
What are you going to do?

838
01:10:34,360 --> 01:10:37,320
I was afraid that the alcohol,

839
01:10:37,320 --> 01:10:41,600
might have accidentally made me do
something from my deepest desires.

840
01:10:42,000 --> 01:10:43,880
Jom, do you want to try making a garland?

841
01:10:45,720 --> 01:10:48,720
Maen is being punished by
the foreign master in the kitchen.

842
01:10:48,720 --> 01:10:49,880
Oh..

843
01:10:50,120 --> 01:10:51,600
Do you know Prik?

844
01:10:51,600 --> 01:10:53,400
I have something important
to discuss with him.

845
01:10:53,400 --> 01:10:55,960
Prik is about to be punished
by Khun Yai's parents.

846
01:10:56,520 --> 01:10:59,520
As for Jom, an accomplice with Prik,

847
01:10:59,520 --> 01:11:00,720
must be punished as well.
